Godswood0264979bcs31kc4j3fnsv3cx734ge3dua8n61272742014-04-16T11:51:30ZThe Snow Prince24099677Minor edit[[File:Winterfell_Godswood.jpg|thumb|300px|The Godswood at [[Winterfell]].]]

'''Godswoods''' are wooded areas, enclosed within a castle's walls, that have been set aside as places of worship and meditation dedicated to the [[Old Gods of the Forest]]. They are centered around a single [[heart tree]], usually a [[weirwood]] tree with a face carved into the trunk.

One such godswood is located in [[Winterfell]].&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Winter is Coming (episode)]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Pointy End]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

The [[Red Keep]] also has a godswood but, being a rather recent castle, it has no weirwood tree.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Two Swords]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
